{"tid":1530990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［廣傳］831太子站被捕者全數控告暴動罪，純粹係白色恐怖！","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T09:27:18.000Z","uid":206523,"like":96,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ce9bc0b492be39724456037aacea4b258ebbfa","tid":1530990,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>#緊急 #廣傳 #長沙灣<br />\n1330 <br />\n831太子站被捕人士 <br />\n全數落控暴動罪 <br />\n將於1430於西九龍裁判法庭 一號庭提堂<br />\n地址為: 長沙灣通洲街501號</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">可以嬲但唔可以驚！<br />\n班狗的目的就係高調控告暴動！<br />\n控告同成功入罪係兩回事！<br />\n無當場斷正的話根本無可能入到暴動罪，賭Ｊ最後最多只會改控非法集結！<br />\n佢就係想製造白色恐怖比其他人睇，去遊行就可能會當暴動！<br />\n就算明知告唔入都要搞你一排等你唔比出街！<br />\n呢個係事實，要穩定軍心，廣傳！！！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c0bed83ae9741eefb0c92ea399c4d83d71a1a275","tid":1530990,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:02:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e56621994636cbbacfa72e865f154a9936f1b277","tid":1530990,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cb480dfb22cdf5bd91d889b7571e09494ad37a1","tid":1530990,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14f56b7a8eb70894414ba8973a4404bb422a79e7","tid":1530990,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:02:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6de28f2b43e2c8a85ecd165f23c1a371b7614332","tid":1530990,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:02:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c29bb5ba27550d04de35c149f7ee7662ff83a181","tid":1530990,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"有24個鐘比佢地生豬肉"},{"pid":"67e6c1f5071904648f8fbdf14df07e27ed8f1788","tid":1530990,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<